
Initial features
----------------

 Just enough to be useful -- so people can start sharing recipes on-line.

       - basic branding of website.

       - searchable database of 'published' recipes.

       - users can create accounts for themselves, write their own
         recipes and submit them for approval/publishing (by Eff)

       - each recipes can have a threaded discussion attached

       - allow users to rate recipes (so recipes can have an 'average
         score', like amazon book reviews)



Future, Advanced Features
-------------------------

       - ability to group recipes into menus, and generate shopping
         lists.

       - allow users to enter food likes/dislikes/allergies

